305
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:22,400
Me temo que tendrás que cancelarlo.

306
00:19:23,390 --> 00:19:24,978
Encontrar una salida.

307
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:33,219
Lo siento Howard.

308
00:19:34,209 --> 00:19:35,459
Realmente lo siento.

309
00:19:42,870 --> 00:19:44,440
<i>El rollo diez Sr. Hughes.</i>

310
00:19:50,450 --> 00:19:51,670
